{"tid":1992463,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步撚 VS 行山撚，邊個安全一些和健康一些","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T07:46:00.000Z","uid":149978,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cefbd92fda47a82576279af6de2c0343095ce7","tid":1992463,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"跑步撚<br />\n<br />\n1）身體唔舒服時，可以隨時暫停。<br />\n2）去廁所都容易些。<br />\n3）計時容易。<br />\n4）條路較寬。<br />\n5）冇行山咁多動物或山賊有機會攻擊你。<br />\n6）唔會跌落山。<br />\n<br />\n行山撚：<br />\n1）空氣質素極佳<br />\n2）視野非常廣寬<br />\n3）目標性較強<br />\n4）上山自動push你做運動要較高強度，冇咁易放棄休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跑步撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行山撚"},{"pid":"71528f7145cc665d89dd114464bd86aa0cdc5bab","tid":1992463,"uid":1941,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"跑山撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2182c383ecfda16a496c7b8ac8ddfa6b55a58bc","tid":1992463,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"跑步 全民練跑<br />\n<br />\n[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dae2bf3ca76a75a96c7b87cb9d8263dc4bacbff4","tid":1992463,"uid":119932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"71528f7145cc665d89dd114464bd86aa0cdc5bab","tid":1992463,"uid":1941,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"跑山撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"6e94c77211de443f8a53ebe5479e424dd7ffd531","tid":1992463,"uid":202412,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"山賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd7249ed3b2c69a627445c4b219f9d140b397c6","tid":1992463,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:31:46.000Z","msg":"行山風險比較高<br />\n<br />\n試過良田坳 靈渡山中間肚痛<br />\n要自己爆條路 <br />\n<br />\n直接落藍地"},{"pid":"fbc349f0f974c9cf81b6fb23cd9dc37bf5f5eccf","tid":1992463,"uid":161136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔做哂兩樣佢.....<br />\n<br />\n利申跑開長跑....全馬都跑過<br />\n近幾年都開始鐘意行山....<br />\n早排先行完虎吼石落西狗牙...<br />\n<br />\n跑步係持之以恆....<br />\n行山目標同成功感強....<br />\n<br />\n建議一齊做...由其係亂世.....<br />\n心肺功能好重要！"}]}